200.description: Get a completion from Bard AI

parameters.name: promptWeight
parameters.description: The weight of the prompt. Higher values mean more influence on the generated image.

parameters.name: image_strength
parameters.description: How much influence the init_image has on the diffusion process. Values close to 1 will yield images very similar to the init_image while values close to 0 will yield images wildly different than the init_image. The behavior of this is meant to mirror DreamStudio's "Image Strength" slider.

parameters.name: cfg_scale
parameters.description: How strictly the diffusion process adheres to the prompt text (higher values keep your image closer to your prompt)

parameters.name: steps
parameters.description: Number of diffusion steps to run

prompt.description: Prompt to generate image from text

cfg_scale.description: How strictly the diffusion process adheres to the prompt text (higher values keep your image closer to your prompt)

steps.description: Number of diffusion steps to run

max_length.description: Maximum number of tokens to generate. A word is generally 2-3 tokens

temperature.description: Adjusts randomness of outputs, greater than 1 is random and 0 is deterministic, 0.75 is a good starting value.

top_p.description: When decoding text, samples from the top p percentage of most likely tokens; lower to ignore less likely tokens

repetition_penalty.description: Penalty for repeated words in generated text; 1 is no penalty, values greater than 1 discourage repetition, less than 1 encourage it.

length_penalty.description: Increasing the length_penalty parameter above 1.0 will cause the model to favor longer sequences, while decreasing it below 1.0 will cause the model to favor shorter sequences.

no_repeat_ngram_size.description: If set to int > 0, all ngrams of size no_repeat_ngram_size can only occur once. 0

seed.description: Set seed for reproducible outputs. Set to -1 for random seed.

max_new_tokens.description: Maximum number of tokens to generate. A word is generally 2-3 tokens

system_prompt.description: System prompt to send to Llama v2. This is prepended to the prompt and helps guide system behavior

min_new_tokens.description: Minimum number of tokens to generate. To disable, set to -1. A word is generally 2-3 tokens.
